{"tid":818341,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"搶 iPhone Xs Max 無 iReserve？小炒王：疑改玩法趕絕炒家","createTime":"2018-09-14T04:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:07:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7210d262047c5153bb60f3d26c12509a44b8651c","tid":818341,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"iPhone XS Max 開搶在即！先達唔少炒家都認為首批有得炒，想首日拎倒貨嘅話，好多炒家都會用 iReserve 方式訂機。但今年 Apple 疑似出新招趕絕炒家。<br />\n<br />\n今年 Apple 並未提及 iReserve 玩法，但小記參考 Apple 香港官網的其他 iPhone 型號，以試買 iPhone 8 為例，Apple Online Store 的訂購方法除了一般送貨上門外，亦可到零售店取機，惟用戶必須網上先付款，預計 iPhone XS 及 iPhone XS Max 今日開賣也會採用相同的「變種版」iReserve 方法。"},{"pid":"1a87e26946d97132c36a73b75efca03e237b58ef","tid":818341,"uid":115082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"又係你呀？"},{"pid":"5e9503b2d0f3e9944cb68c6669126d7941aa4bbb","tid":818341,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=9n63ACnIhs93NpSLY7Y4x%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=99440265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者向小炒王詢問此事，他說道：「吓，又改玩法趕絕炒家？即時俾錢預約落舖拎，隨時無退路喎！」以往，不少炒家玩 iReserve 都係「㩒左先」，等睇當日真係有炒價先去 Apple Retail Store 即場購買。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Apple 並非首次向炒家作出規限，自 iPhone 7 起，港澳地區購買的 Apple 產品均不設退貨。"},{"pid":"4e0df0472bab308501e99700bbcc5430170b6abb","tid":818341,"uid":106477,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"乜撚野趕絕炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賊喊捉賊 d用家無機買又叫乜 on99"},{"pid":"4bf029449e076130313a9542fc816f96a063e2e1","tid":818341,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知以為葉榮添<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af28bd82f24dbc97929f9fd2311b9e1a0972b0f7","tid":818341,"uid":5058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241e69de99238b9ebb4b1473bce01f07d78d0e48","tid":818341,"uid":78203,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"點解人地要俾你炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到炒機係老馮咁<br />\n唔俾你炒係剝削<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea98985f72a6328c74969ce9b0b42db0e7529b2","tid":818341,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"呢件小炒王上次柒左  仲出黎把撚呀"},{"pid":"2bacbbf45e95b57545433ba1714205ac775a7961","tid":818341,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"好呀好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f91257245060eb924abe033b8582feafe8ba085","tid":818341,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea98985f72a6328c74969ce9b0b42db0e7529b2","tid":818341,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"呢件小炒王上次柒左  仲出黎把撚呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"咩事？"},{"pid":"4b4995f5e37de302f1e4a6e9f2a83c278763f451","tid":818341,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f